subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
lead_paragraph: Calipari’s five starting freshmen, all N.B.A. prospects, flopped in the regular season, and he apologizes for that, but it is ancient history with Kentucky in the Round of 16.
